property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    "RFXDocument"."SourcingProject_ID" AS "SourcingProject",
    'BiddingEnds_' || "AuditEntry"."ID" AS "ID",
    "RFXDocument"."ID" AS "RfxDocument",
    "AuditEntry"."TimeCreated" as "Time"
FROM "o_custom_AuditEntry" as "AuditEntry"
JOIN "o_custom_RFXDocument" as "RFXDocument" ON 1 = 1
    AND "AuditEntry"."ContextObjectInternalId" = "RFXDocument"."InternalId"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "AuditEntry"."TemplateActionNameDefaultStringTranslation" LIKE 'Bidding ends%'
    AND "AuditEntry"."TimeCreated" IS NOT NULL

    AND "RFXDocument"."InternalId" = "Bid"."ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentId"
    AND "RFXDocument"."DocumentVersion" = "Bid"."ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentVersion"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "AuditEntry"."TemplateActionNameDefaultStringTranslation" LIKE 'Bidding ends%'
    AND "AuditEntry"."TimeCreated" IS NOT NULL
